COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 631, L.D. 971
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment replaces the bill and changes the title. It amends the law regarding
33 checking baitfish traps by increasing the amount of time permitted between baitfish trap
44 checks from 7 calendar days to 21 calendar days from November 1st to April 1st. The
55 amendment also directs the Department of Inland Fisheries and Wildlife to submit a report
66 concerning this change to the joint standing committee of the Legislature having
77 jurisdiction over inland fisheries and wildlife matters by January 1, 2029 and authorizes
88 the committee to report out a bill based on the report to the 134th Legislature in 2029.
99 FISCAL NOTE REQUIRED
1100 (See attached)
